trans-unit.source: Provides a set of utility functions for interpreting performance counter data.
trans-unit.target: 解释性能计数器数据，提供了一套实用工具函数。

trans-unit.source: Computes the calculated value of a single raw counter sample.
trans-unit.target: 计算单个原始计数器样本的计算的值。

trans-unit.source: The ComputeCounterValue method overload returns meaningful results only for performance counters of the following <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>: - <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> - <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> - <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> - <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> - <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> For other counter types, this overload always returns a value of 0 (zero).
trans-unit.target: 方法重载方法返回有意义 ComputeCounterValue 仅的以下性能计数器结果<xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>:- <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>- <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>- <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>- <xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>-<xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>对于其他计数器类型，此重载方法始终返回值为 0 （零）。</xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> </xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> </xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> </xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> </xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType> </xref:System.Diagnostics.PerformanceCounterType>
